Working on National TV is itself a work of high grandeur. This splendid calibre has been shown by our very own Rashmi Boruah..

She has been featured in one of India's top rated Crime Soap *Savdhan India*.

Without limiting her capabilities, she has also been featured in *Crime Alert* for *Dangal* and *Arunodoi* for *DD National*.

Not only in the fields of Indian Serials, *Rashmi* has a long background in the Advertisement world. Some of them are:
*Oppo*
*Vicco Turmeric*
*UV Cross*
*VIBGYOR School*
*Pavitram Jewelleries* etc.

I was immensely grateful to get the chance to charm this beautiful young lady as her Makeup Artist.

Brace yourself, cause bridal photos are coming soon.
